window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Logan has come a long way already, but he's far from done.</p> <p>The Coven King prophecy is a sure thing, and every witch in Fresco City knows it by now. What's more, even the coastal super covens are growing aware. They're not happy. Yet. Give them time to warm up to him, though.</p> <p>Logan is a magnanimous king, after all, and his witches live to serve him. The Rising Star Coven is on its way up in the witching world, and no one can say for sure just how far that star will rise.</p> <p>One thing's for sure...neither the monsters he defeats nor the witches he conquers can stop...the rise of the one true Coven King.</p>"; 
